{
  "stem": "20616.2",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I started to pray twice a day and after each meal.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And I remember my father had ham at the table and I took it once and I threw it out of the window.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] And he got very upset.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "He said, look, if you don't want to eat ham, that's your business.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "But you're not going to tell us what to do.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "So-- [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] I-- in fact, another thing is I tore toilet paper ahead of time before the Sabbath so I wouldn't have to-- I was really almost fanatically religious for a while, but that subsided.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And-- but I was still very much aware of politically and started to be interested when we were talking about the possible emigration.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And in fact, at first my father said, no, they're not going to touch me, I'm a World War I veteran, I've got the Iron Cross and I'm respected here.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They're not going to touch me.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But soon we found out that that was not to be the case and my parents-- my mother-- at my mother's urging that we made some preparation with the idea of emigrating.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Where to?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I wanted to go to Palestine when the question came and I joined [INAUDIBLE], the Communist youth group.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And my father said, no.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I can't see myself as a farmer and I'm going to try to come to the United States.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In fact, my father came to the United States as a visitor.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I believe it was either 1930-- I think it was 1930-- end of 1935.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I'm not sure as far as the date is concerned.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he came here with the idea of trying to get an affidavit.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
